tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE feedback_on_ethical_implications_of_AI (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  stakeholder_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE users_feedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE stakeholders_feedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ai_applications (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    application_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ethical_implications (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    implication_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)
